  Added ssl USE flag.

*mew-3.2-r1 (18 Jun 2003)

  25 Aug 2003; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> mew-3.2-r1.ebuild,
  mew-3.2.ebuild:
  Removed for security risk with skey implementation.  This problem
  is fixed in mew 3.3 and doesn't exist in mew 3.1

  03 Jul 2003; Masatomo Nakano <nakano@gentoo.org> mew-3.2-r1.ebuild:
  marked stable for x86,ppc

  18 Jun 2003; Masatomo Nakano <nakano@gentoo.org> mew-3.2-r1.ebuild:
  fixed bug about man path

